2. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with natural language generation from video, which falls under the scope of computational linguistics. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the fusion of audio and visual modalities, which is a topic in multimedia research. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a novel deep learning framework for video captioning, which falls under the scope of machine learning. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper deals with the development of an AI system for video captioning, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence.
